| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0533 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 100cb8cd-622a-554a-a742-6a5e2da8dce9"
